title: Lunchbox’s Bathroom Confessions + Derek Hough Stops By For The Friday Morning Conversation
itunes:title: Lunchbox’s Bathroom Confessions + Derek Hough Stops By For The Friday Morning Conversation
description:
While in a bathroom stall at the airport, Lunchbox pulled out his hidden mic and decided to make some “Bathroom Confessions” to other people using the restroom. Also, Derek Hough (Dancing With The Stars, World Of Dance) stops by for the Friday Morning Conversation.
